[INSTALLATION]



- Unrar with you favorite archiver, such as WinRar

- Uninstall previous versions.

- Install the software.

- Make your computer offline.

- Run the keygen.

- Select AmpliTube product in Keygen.

- Click Register this computer.

- IF not Activated.

- Run Authorization Manager.

- Start offline authorization.

- Save authorization file.

- Click "Get From Authorization Request File"
and open a request file (.html).
Or input DigitalID to the keygen by hand.
You can find in the *.html file.
" <input type="hidden" name="DigitalID"
value="XXXXXXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXXXXXX"> "

- Push "Generate For Other Computers"
and save the authorization file.

- Open the generated file with Authorization Manager.

- Ok, It's Activated!
